# Frontend (Hotwire)

## Views (ERB)

- Prefer Rails helpers and partials; keep partials focused and named with a leading underscore.
- Turbo: use `turbo_frame_tag` / `turbo_stream` patterns consistent with existing screens; match `dom_id` targets to what controllers broadcast or render.
- Forms: use `form_with`, appropriate `data-turbo` / `local` behavior aligned with the rest of the app.

## Stimulus

- One concern per controller file under `app/javascript/controllers/`; register in `controllers/index.js` when adding new controllers.
- Use `data-*-target`, `data-action`, and values; avoid large imperative DOM manipulation unless necessary — prefer declarative actions.

## Importmap

- New JS dependencies: pin with `bin/importmap pin <package>` (or project’s documented flow), not ad-hoc remote scripts.
